headline: Wells Fargo Foundation Awards $3.2 Million in Grants to Empower North Minneapolis
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, CA / ACCESS Newswire / September 18, 2025 / The Wells Fargo Foundation announced today $3.2 million in grant funding to help accelerate affordable housing access, small business growth, and workforce development in North Minneapolis. ...
